	Unequal railroad operation
	Only one dessent on the supreme court
1909 Springfield Race Riot
	Most significant race riot
	Lynched a black man
	Destroyed black property
	Leads to the establishment of the NAACP
By 1900, only about 1\% of blacks graduate high school compared to 5-6\% of whites
Booker T Washington
	Establishes Tuskegee Institute
	Idea: Blacks should prove themselves and the barriers will fall
W.E.B Du Bois
	First black PhD (from Harvard)
	Finds he can't get a job
	Becomes radicalized
	Finally gets a job but gets blocked, works at Atlanta University
	Niagra Manifesto
		Political power is the key
		Need it now
	Du Bois will be the only black staff of NAACP for a while
